# 11.47: Issue as a Subgenre, with Steven Barnes 

Listen [here](http://www.writingexcuses.com/2016/11/20/11-47-issue-as-a-subgenre-with-steven-barnes/). 

**Prompt:** In our first Elemental Issue episode we asked you to read a magazine. Your homework, then: Write a monologue from the POV of a member of that magazine’s target audience. Pair this with another subgenre. 
